_games\" />| away = Newton\n| try1 = [[Karl Ifwersen]] 2, Collins\n| con1 = [[Karl Ifwersen]] 2\n| pen1 = [[Karl Ifwersen]]\n| try2 = Clark, Alan Blakey, Len Farrant\n| con2 = Clark\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Auckland Domain\n| attendance =\n| referee = Whitley\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 29 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = North Shore\n| score = 8\u201315\n| report =<ref name=\"interesting_games\" />| away = City\n| try1 =\n| con1 =\n| pen1 = Jack Paul 2 & 2 marks\n| try2 = [[Albert Asher]] 3\n| con2 = [[Ernie Asher]] 3\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Devonport Domain\n| attendance =\n| referee = Fielding\n}}\n\n======Round 5======\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 19 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = City\n| score = 16\u201310\n| report =<ref name=\"first_round\">{{cite news\n| title =First round Concluded/Ponsonby LeadingGrafton's First Defeat/Newton's Initial Win/Ponsonby's Easy Victory\n| page =4\n| work=[[The New Zealand Herald]]| volume=LII| issue=15949\n| date = 21 June 1915\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19150621.2.14\n| accessdate = 10 August 2019}}</ref>| away = Grafton\n| try1 = George Asher 2, [[Albert Asher]] 2\n| con1 = [[Ernie Asher]]\n| pen1 = [[Ernie Asher]]\n| try2 = J McGregor 2\n| con2 =\n| pen2 = [[Karl Ifwersen]] & 1 mark\n| stadium = Victoria Park # 1\n| attendance =\n| referee = R Benson\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 19 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Newton\n| score = 18\u20136\n| report =<ref name=\"first_round\" />| away = Otahuhu\n| try1 = Bowen, Jim Bennett, Biggs, Potier\n| con1 = Jim Bennett 2\n| pen1 = Tobin\n| try2 = Fisher, Spence\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park # 3\n| attendance =\n| referee = Ferguson\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 19 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 18\u20130\n| report =<ref name=\"first_round\" />| away = North Shore\n| try1 = V McCallum 2\n| con1 = A Cross 2\n| pen1 = A Cross 3, S Jones\n| try2 =\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 